Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:03.09,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}We spend days resonating with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:08.05,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}I'm trying to find a suitable name for this piling up relation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.43,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}But calling it a "bond" is too simple
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:18.52,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}It doesn't represent this overflowing emotions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.77,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}In the same place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.90,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}with the same point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:29.61,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}So we won't look down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:35.12,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}I want to share the same burden with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:40.84,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}not to just become an existence to carry everything yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:46.09,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}When we're back to back, we're on the same level
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:51.51,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}Even our breathing rhythm matches each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.27,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}These actions we took without looking back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:59.60,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}is a substitute for a pinky promise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:04.15,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\frx450\t(0,200,\frx360)}It'll reach me, always
