Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:41.98,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}You tell me about your what hypothetical story, in a comfortable voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:45.52,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}along with your idealistic thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:49.57,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}I took a glance at your fed up expression from the side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:57.74,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Suddenly my heart hurts from our special distance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:04.87,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}I can't hold my pulsing heart anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:09.25,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Inside this vague love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.80,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}I call your name, who I want to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.63,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}It's strange isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:20.85,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}In the future between you and me, it'll be filled with colorful days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:28.17,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Yearning for uncertainty, is a beauty of transience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:35.70,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Every time I spell it, it made me want to hold this feeling to be honest to you
